title: iCarly's 'i' Font
content:
Hey guys,

I've been looking for this font for a long time, think you can help?

I've posted on WTF Forums but had no luck.

Here are the links to the font samples.

author: cjmoon95

comments.content: Reminds me of [Sauna](http://web.archive.org/web/20100928095509/http:/www.identifont.com/show?20DR), which is not it.
